## 1. Updated System Architecture

### Before (Current MVP)

```
User Question → Embedding → PGVector Cosine Search → Top 5 Chunks → LLM → Full Response
```

### After (Production-Grade)

```
User Question
    ├── Embedding → PGVector Cosine Similarity (Semantic Search)
    └── PostgreSQL ts_vector → BM25 Full-Text Search (Keyword Search)
         │
         ├── Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF) → Merged Top K Results
         │
         └── Context → Gemini 2.5 Flash (Streaming) → Token-by-Token SSE → Frontend
                                                          │
                                                    Stored in DB
                                                          │
                                                    RAGAS Evaluation Pipeline
                                                    (Precision, Recall, Faithfulness)
```

