### RAGAS Evaluation Flow

```
Evaluation Pipeline:
                                                    
  +-------------------+    +----------------------+   
  | Eval Dataset      |    | User's Documents     |   
  | (5 Q&A pairs)     |    | (Uploaded PDFs)      |   
  +--------+----------+    +-----------+----------+   
           |                           |                
           |    +----------------------v----------+     
           |    |  Hybrid Retrieval Engine         |     
           |    |  (BM25 + Vector Search)          |     
           |    +--------------+------------------+     
           |                   | Retrieved Contexts     
           |    +--------------v------------------+     
           |    |  Gemini 2.5 Flash LLM           |     
           |    |  (Generate Answers)              |     
           |    +--------------+------------------+     
           |                   | Generated Answers      
           |                   |                        
    +------v-------------------v--------------------+      
    |         RAGAS Evaluation Engine                |      
    |                                                |      
    |  Question + Context + Answer + Truth           |      
    |           |                                    |      
    |  +-------------+  +--------------+             |      
    |  | Context     |  | Context      |             |      
    |  | Precision   |  | Recall       |             |      
    |  +-------------+  +--------------+             |      
    |  +-------------+  +--------------+             |      
    |  | Faithfulness|  | Answer       |             |      
    |  |             |  | Relevancy    |             |      
    |  +-------------+  +--------------+             |      
    +--------------------+---------------------------+      
                         |                            
               +---------v----------+                 
               |  Score Report      |                 
               |  Precision: 0.87   |                 
               |  Recall:    0.72   |                 
               |  Faithful:  0.93   |                 
               |  Relevant:  0.88   |                 
               +--------------------+                 
```

