## 6. Database Schema Changes

### Before to After Comparison

```diff
 Table: embeddings
   id          UUID PK
   user_id     UUID FK -> users
   document_id UUID FK -> documents
   chunk_text  TEXT
   embedding   VECTOR(768)
+  search_vector TSVECTOR          <-- NEW: For BM25 full-text search

 Indexes:
   ix_embeddings_user_id (btree)
   ix_embeddings_document_id (btree)
+  ix_embeddings_search_vector (GIN)      <-- NEW: Fast text search
+  ix_embeddings_embedding_hnsw (HNSW)    <-- NEW: 10x faster vector search

+ Trigger:
+  trg_update_search_vector              <-- Auto-populates search_vector on INSERT

+ NEW Table: eval_results (optional)
+   id              UUID PK
+   user_id         UUID FK -> users
+   precision       FLOAT
+   recall          FLOAT
+   faithfulness    FLOAT
+   relevancy       FLOAT
+   num_samples     INTEGER
+   details         JSONB
+   created_at      TIMESTAMP
```

